                <td bgcolor="#000000" valign="top"><font color="#FFFFFF" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;04/11/2003&nbsp;: 5:41:31 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> After I wrote that last post, I saw Absor's post on this board.  The issue is discussed pretty well in the other thread.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=611383" target="_blank">Sleppen Slyden, Defiler of Cazic-Thule</a> <br /><br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=611457" target="_blank">Serreatus Foestriker, Warlord of Rallos Zek</a></span></font></td>
